<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Novo contato</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f8;
            font-family: 'Inter', Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        .wrapper {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 40px 12px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #111827, #0f172a);
        }
        .card {
            max-width: 640px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 28px;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 60px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.25);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .hero {
            padding: 40px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.2), transparent 55%),
                        radial-gradient(circle at right, rgba(129, 140, 248, 0.25), transparent 50%),
                        #0f172a;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .hero h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 26px;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .hero p {
            margin-top: 12px;
            font-size: 15px;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 32px 40px 40px;
            color: #0f172a;
        }
        .info-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
            gap: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }
        .info-card {
            border: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
            border-radius: 18px;
            padding: 18px 20px;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
        }
        .info-card span {
            display: block;
            font-size: 11px;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #64748b;
        }
        .info-card strong {
            display: block;
            margin-top: 8px;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #0f172a;
            word-wrap: break-word;
        }
        .message-block {
            border-radius: 22px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e0f2fe, #e0e7ff);
            padding: 28px;
        }
        .message-block span {
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 11px;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
            color: #0369a1;
        }
        .message-block p {
            margin-top: 14px;
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: #0f172a;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 28px 30px 36px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #94a3b8;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .hero, .content {
                padding: 28px;
            }
            .card {
                border-radius: 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="hero">
                <h1>Mensagem Recebida</h1>
                <p>Um novo contato foi enviado pelo site. Confira os detalhes abaixo.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                <div class="info-grid">
                    <div class="info-card">
                        <span>Nome</span>
                        <strong>{{ name }}</strong>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-card">
                        <span>E-mail</span>
                        <strong>{{ sender_email }}</strong>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-card">
                        <span>Telefone</span>
                        <strong>{{ phone }}</strong>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-card">
                        <span>Enviado em</span>
                        <strong>{{ submitted_at|date('d/m/Y H:i') }}</strong>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="message-block">
                    <span>Mensagem</span>
                    <p>{{ message|nl2br }}</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="footer">
                Você recebeu este e-mail porque o formulário de contato do site foi utilizado. Responda diretamente ao remetente para continuar a conversa.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
